Title: Taylor Swift: The 1989 World Tour Live
Actors: Taylor Swift, Uzo Aduba, Lily Aldridge, Abigail Anderson
Plot: Filmed in front of 76,000 fans at the ANZ Stadium in Sydney, Australia, "The 1989 World Tour Live" captures Taylor Swift's entire performance while also mixing in behind-the-scene, rehearsal, and special guest footage from her 1989 Tour.
